      • DatabaseEntry

        public DatabaseEntry​(java.lang.String id,
                     java.lang.String dummyId,
                     java.lang.String username,
                     java.lang.String description,
                     java.lang.String url,
                     java.lang.String password,
                     java.lang.String creationDate,
                     java.lang.String lastUpdate,
                     java.lang.String note)
        the contructor
        Parameters:
        id - an id set by the database
        dummyId - the index of all the entries out of the database. it is used to have a better display in tableView
        username - username
        description - type of account
        url - url
        password - a password (encrypted)
        creationDate - date of creation of the entry (getDateTime() from this class)
        lastUpdate - date of last update (first time is the same date as date of creation)
        note - a note of the user.
